    "difficultyTier": "hardest",
    "_halfwayNote": "HALFWAY-DEMORGAN MISCONCEPTION ITEM. Correct application: NOT((A AND B) OR C) = NOT(A AND B) AND NOT C = (NOT A OR NOT B) AND NOT C, table [1,0,1,0,1,0,0,0]. Halfway error: NOT(A AND B) OR NOT C = (NOT A OR NOT B) OR NOT C = NOT A OR NOT B OR NOT C, table [1,1,1,1,1,1,1,0]. Off-by-4-cells. Designed to catch learners who distribute NOT but keep OR instead of AND."
  },
  {
