    "_halfwayNote": "HALFWAY-DEMORGAN MISCONCEPTION ITEM. Correct application: NOT(A OR (B AND C)) = NOT A AND NOT(B AND C) = NOT A AND (NOT B OR NOT C), table [1,1,1,0,0,0,0,0]. Halfway error: NOT A OR NOT(B AND C) = NOT A OR (NOT B OR NOT C) = NOT A OR NOT B OR NOT C, table [1,1,1,1,1,1,1,0]. Off-by-3-cells. Designed to catch learners who flip NOT but keep OR instead of AND on outer operator."
  }
